      <frequency>few</frequency>
      <avalancheSize>2</avalancheSize>
    </avalancheProblem>
    <weatherForecast/>
    <avalancheActivity>
      <highlights>In particular on steep sunny slopes there will be an increase in the danger of moist and wet avalanches.</highlights>
      <comment>In particular on steep slopes small and medium-sized moist and wet avalanches are possible as a consequence of warming during the day and solar radiation. Slab avalanches are still possible.</comment>
    </avalancheActivity>
    <snowpackStructure>
      <comment>The solar radiation will give rise to increasing moistening of the snowpack in all aspects. These conditions will cause a weakening of the snowpack. This applies in particular on steep sunny slopes. The surface of the snowpack will soften during the day.</comment>
    </snowpackStructure>
    <travelAdvisory/>
